Class Rocket

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.monash.fit2099.engine.Actor
      • game.characters.Character
        • game.characters.Rocket
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Printable, Skilled, java.lang.Comparable<Actor>

    public class Rocket
extends Character
    A rocket character. Can have parts added, or will send a player to a paired rocket if finished. Ends the game if Yugo is in the player's inventory.
